{"type": "article", "id": 30049, "title": "小鸟削皮器", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-24T22:51:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160724213839MvdCDGK5Az3QjY0R.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>第一眼看到 Tweet 时你或许还会纳闷它到底是用来干什么的，实际上这个就像真的鸟儿一样直立的小物并不是什么装饰品，而是设计师 <a href=\"http://dorcarmon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dor Carmon</a> 为特拉维夫品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 设计的一款折叠型的削皮器。Tweet 侧面的三角形凸起就像是鸟喙，转轴则构成了眼睛的部分，整体造型小巧又富有趣味。折叠设计体现出了它的便携优势并且可以保护刀片不受污染，放在厨房内也不会占用过多空间。这款削皮器将于下月正式开始销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724213855C4l6pZOB37W1RLET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724213854tU2ZBQbvDjS9ngFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.864303\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724213854dDCFtOlUx4wHZe0m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724213855P21lJhG9HYoceRxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}